#### Step-by-step to Fix:
1. In the function, the bug is found in the while loop. The line text.substring(end); causes the loop to stop prematurely. Fix the bug by using the end index as the end of the loop.
2. To print the text in the arrayList, we use the for loop. The bug is found in the for loop. The line lines.add(line); is adding an extra line to the ArrayList. To fix this bug, we use the StringBuilder instead of the ArrayList.


